Warding is a lie, there is only farming;
Through farming, I gain levels;
Through levels, I gain kills;
Through kills, I gain power;
Through power, I gain victory;
Through victory, my elo is risen,
The Silver shall free me.
-The Code of the Silver

There is no Elo Hell, there is MMR.
There is no ignorance, there is knowledge.
There is no pushing, there is laning.
There is no farming, there is teamfighting.
There is no gank, there is the ward.
-The Diamond Code
